# Vercel cron runs every 15 minutes; the app dispatches only users whose dailyPushTime
# falls inside the current window and have not already been sent that issue.
# For real email delivery, set either Resend or SMTP.
# For WeChat / IM push, point WECHAT_BRIDGE_URL or IM_BRIDGE_URL to your bridge webhook.
